41:31.679 --> 41:35.083
<i>Be a tragedy if you
never met Christopher.</i>

41:35.117 --> 41:37.319
<i>Never got to hold him.</i>

41:39.086 --> 41:40.355
<i>Because, truth be told,</i>

41:40.389 --> 41:42.255
